query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 5
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('aggregation-framework',
'asp.net-membership',
'drupal-6',
'ember.js',
'export',
'notepad++',
'persistence',
'putty',
'query-optimization',
'return-value',
'sql-delete',
'text-files',
'text-to-speech',
'unity-container',
'youtube')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000 group by t1.name;
